WEBVTT

00:11:29.498 --> 00:11:33.451
and pay the shop for using the telephone
and have your phone call.

00:11:33.475 --> 00:11:36.164
So you didn't make phone calls
just whenever you fancied.

00:11:36.188 --> 00:11:37.339
Alan: Oh, no.

00:11:37.363 --> 00:11:39.133
Woman: (Coughs) Oh, sorry.

00:11:39.157 --> 00:11:40.426
(Coughs)

00:11:40.450 --> 00:11:41.776
Excuse me about that.

00:11:41.800 --> 00:11:43.499
You had to, you know,

00:11:43.523 --> 00:11:46.748
confine your phone calls
to the absolute essentials.

00:11:47.141 --> 00:11:52.788
And now, here I am, sitting in my own home
in my dressing gown still,

00:11:52.812 --> 00:11:55.783
and using the telephone,
isn't it wonderful?

00:11:55.807 --> 00:11:58.309
Alan: It is. (Laughter)

00:11:58.886 --> 00:12:02.283
SA: And that's not untypical of a call
we might receive at our helpline.